  "1736270": {
    "name": "They Are Coming!",
    "steam_appid": 1736270,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736270/extras/40b925709046b98e79cb2c299ffaa4ae.avif?t=1754628147\" width=600 height=85 /></span><br>阿登省，1944年。美国人称作“阿登战役（The Battle of the Bulge）”的战事渐渐停歇，而纳粹也用光了瓦斯。盟军的空军将纳粹的军队猛击到土地里。这次战败令德意志帝国做出绝望之举，释放自己的奇迹武器试图扭转战局。饥饿，饥饿的丧尸们出现了。<br><br>好吧，或者说，最开始只有“一只”丧尸。一路撕咬吞食，穿过盟军，纳粹，还有你所遇到的每一个人，直达胜利，这取决于你。将不死的快乐和大脑的美味散播到阿登省森林之外（或就此而言，二战）。<br><br>谁知道现代有什么样美味的人类呢？谁又知道未来会有什么样的呢？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736270/extras/ec51e36b41c26add75abe95ebe1f27c4.avif?t=1754628147\" width=600 height=85 /></span><br>丧尸为一件事情而存在，且只为这件事而存在。那就是吞食人类，或者说，吞食人类的脑子。带上一只丧尸，并“招募”一整个丧尸群以掌控世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736270/extras/0b2d401dfaed331657d15e2aa861690d.avif?t=1754628147\" width=600 height=85 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736270/extras/2d41853786cb6389b88188f18df22290.poster.avif?t=1754628147\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736270/extras/2d41853786cb6389b88188f18df22290.webm?t=1754628147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736270/extras/2d41853786cb6389b88188f18df22290.mp4?t=1754628147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>有些人类绝不会束手就擒，乖乖成为美餐！躲开机枪、迫击炮、坦克炮弹还有人类为让贪婪的丧尸远离自己美味的灰质而在丧尸们前进路上诸多战争。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736270/extras/122ac21b440720f1da6168d5e9fcf45f.avif?t=1754628147\" width=600 height=85 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736270/extras/5f26f838f84324f70fb2c11c77433a17.poster.avif?t=1754628147\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736270/extras/5f26f838f84324f70fb2c11c77433a17.webm?t=1754628147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736270/extras/5f26f838f84324f70fb2c11c77433a17.mp4?t=1754628147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>每个场景都满是可遭遇并咀嚼其坚韧组织的人类。每个场景也有很多秘密和挑战等待发现，和你在路上吞食的朋友一起发现这些秘密和挑战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736270/extras/5b7c5bdef8756bcf3300e1268416d1ef.avif?t=1754628147\" width=600 height=85 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736270/extras/da0969a49c77076f499330f5e9b6bebb.poster.avif?t=1754628147\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736270/extras/da0969a49c77076f499330f5e9b6bebb.webm?t=1754628147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736270/extras/da0969a49c77076f499330f5e9b6bebb.mp4?t=1754628147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>所吞食的一切加起来就得到最后分数和丧尸群的进化情况。优化高效率且势不可挡的策略以吞食所有残存的有机物并最终灭绝人类。",
